1.0.1.name: wordpress/dynamic-plugin
1.0.1.description:
Please, send us your feedback!

Features

  • Multilanguage

  • Build with this plugin:

    • Newsletter list

    • Search engine: for your products, services, some cool stuff. Anything you would like to enable smart search on it

    • Contact form

    • Survey

    • Quiz

    • Some message board

    • Special registration form

    • Feedback

  • Use multiple types of fields in your forms

    • Single-line text

    • Rich Text Editor

    • Drop-down list

    • Date picker

    • Hidden field

    • Checkbox

    • File

    • Image

    • Text Area

  • Set required fields and unique fields

  • Get email notifications after item inserted

  • Store the collected in
